version_description: I think it sounds close to the studio version of the song.
Without barre chords, but with capo.
This is the version of IDWLF that Taylor sang acoustically at this year's Super Saturday concert. This has the capo on third and is a so much easier chord progression than the original.
There is a riff added for the intro. This tab is tabbed to the original key of the song.
